Ray Lamar JOHNSTON, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-3919 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. October 19, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Petitioner's petition for writ of prohibition is denied. Petitioner's request for oral argument is denied. See Fla. R. App. P. 9.320 ("A request for oral argument shall be in a separate document.").

NORTHCUTT, CASANUEVA, and KELLY, JJ., Concur.
